---
import SiteLayout from '../../layouts/SiteLayout.astro';
import PageHeaderSsg from '../../components/_astro/ssg/PageHeaderSsg.astro';
import containerStyles from '../../components/ui/MaxWidthContainer.module.css';
---

<SiteLayout
  lang="en"
  title="Privacy Policy – ROJEK"
  description="Privacy Policy of ROJEK OKNA I DRZWI Sp. z o.o."
>
  <PageHeaderSsg
    imageSrc="/images/policy/policy-top.webp"
    title="Privacy Policy"
    height={500}
  />

  <main class="legal-page">
    <div class={containerStyles.root} data-max-width-container="true">
      <article class="legal-content">
      <p><strong>ROJEK OKNA I DRZWI Spółka z ograniczoną odpowiedzialnością</strong></p>
      <p><strong>Effective date: 18.02.2026</strong></p>

      <h2>I. General information</h2>
      <p>ROJEK OKNA I DRZWI Spółka z ograniczoną odpowiedzialnością (the “Controller”, the “Company”) attaches particular importance to the protection of privacy and personal data of users of the website:</p>
      <p><a href="https://rojekokna.pl">https://rojekokna.pl</a></p>
      <p>This Privacy Policy sets out the rules for personal data processing in accordance with:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Regulation (EU) 2016/679 of the European Parliament and of the Council (“GDPR”),</li>
        <li>the Personal Data Protection Act,</li>
        <li>provisions concerning the provision of electronic services.</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>II. Data controller</h2>
      <p>The data controller is:</p>
      <p>ROJEK OKNA I DRZWI Spółka z ograniczoną odpowiedzialnością<br />Kryspinów 399<br />32-060 Kryspinów<br />NIP: 9442286185</p>
      <p>In matters related to personal data processing, you can contact us at: <a href="mailto:biuro@rojekokna.pl">biuro@rojekokna.pl</a></p>

      <h2>III. Scope of processed data</h2>
      <p>Depending on how you use the website, we process:</p>
      <h3>1. Data voluntarily provided by the user</h3>
      <p>In particular via the contact form:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>full name (if provided),</li>
        <li>email address,</li>
        <li>phone number,</li>
        <li>project location,</li>
        <li>inquiry content.</li>
      </ul>

      <h3>2. Data collected automatically</h3>
      <ul>
        <li>IP address,</li>
        <li>browser and operating system data,</li>
        <li>approximate location,</li>
        <li>website activity data,</li>
        <li>data stored in cookies.</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>IV. Purposes and legal bases for processing</h2>
      <p>We process personal data for the following purposes:</p>
      <h3>1. Handling inquiries and customer contact</h3>
      <p>Legal basis: Art. 6(1)(b) GDPR (steps prior to entering into a contract) and Art. 6(1)(f) GDPR (legitimate interest of the Controller – communication).</p>
      <h3>2. Entering into and performing a contract</h3>
      <p>Legal basis: Art. 6(1)(b) GDPR</p>
      <h3>3. Compliance with legal obligations (accounting, tax)</h3>
      <p>Legal basis: Art. 6(1)(c) GDPR</p>
      <h3>4. Analytics and statistics (Google Analytics)</h3>
      <p>Legal basis: user consent (Art. 6(1)(a) GDPR). Analytics is activated only after consent for analytical cookies is given.</p>
      <h3>5. Contact form security (Google reCAPTCHA)</h3>
      <p>Legal basis: Art. 6(1)(f) GDPR (legitimate interest – protection against spam and automated attacks).</p>
      <h3>6. Establishing, pursuing or defending legal claims</h3>
      <p>Legal basis: Art. 6(1)(f) GDPR</p>

      <h2>V. Google Analytics</h2>
      <p>The website uses Google Analytics provided by Google LLC.</p>
      <p>Google Analytics uses cookies to analyze how the website is used (number of visits, time spent on the website, traffic sources).</p>
      <p>Data may be transferred outside the European Economic Area (e.g. to the USA) based on GDPR-compliant mechanisms (e.g. Standard Contractual Clauses).</p>
      <p>Details: <a href="https://policies.google.com/privacy">https://policies.google.com/privacy</a></p>

      <h2>VI. Google reCAPTCHA</h2>
      <p>The contact form is protected by Google reCAPTCHA, which safeguards the website against spam and abuse.</p>
      <p>reCAPTCHA may analyze, among others:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>IP address,</li>
        <li>user behavior on the website,</li>
        <li>technical device data.</li>
      </ul>
      <p>Details: <a href="https://policies.google.com/privacy">https://policies.google.com/privacy</a></p>
      <p><a href="https://policies.google.com/terms">https://policies.google.com/terms</a></p>

      <h2>VII. Data recipients</h2>
      <p>Data may be shared only with entities supporting the Controller’s operations, in particular:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>hosting and IT infrastructure providers,</li>
        <li>analytics service providers (Google),</li>
        <li>security service providers (reCAPTCHA),</li>
        <li>accounting office,</li>
        <li>law firm.</li>
      </ul>
      <p>Data is not sold to third parties.</p>

      <h2>VIII. Data retention period</h2>
      <p>We store data:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>contact form data – up to 12 months after communication ends,</li>
        <li>contract-related data – in accordance with tax and accounting regulations,</li>
        <li>analytics data – according to Google Analytics retention settings,</li>
        <li>technical logs – for the period necessary to ensure security.</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>IX. Rights of the data subject</h2>
      <p>Every person has the right to:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>access data,</li>
        <li>rectify data,</li>
        <li>erase data (“right to be forgotten”),</li>
        <li>restrict processing,</li>
        <li>data portability,</li>
        <li>object to processing,</li>
        <li>withdraw consent at any time,</li>
        <li>lodge a complaint with the President of the Personal Data Protection Office (<a href="https://uodo.gov.pl">https://uodo.gov.pl</a>).</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>X. Voluntary provision of data</h2>
      <p>Providing data in the contact form is voluntary, but necessary to receive a response.</p>

      <h2>XI. Changes to the Privacy Policy</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>This Policy may be updated.</li>
        <li>The current version is always available at <a href="https://rojekokna.pl">rojekokna.pl</a>.</li>
      </ul>
      </article>
    </div>
  </main>

  <style>
    .legal-page {
      padding: var(--space-lg) 0 var(--space-xl);
      background: var(--color-background);
    }

    .legal-content {
      max-width: none;
      width: 100%;
      font-family: var(--font-main);
      color: var(--color-text-dark);
    }

    .legal-content h2,
    .legal-content h3 {
      font-family: var(--font-heading);
      color: var(--color-bottle-green);
      font-weight: 500;
      line-height: 1.3;
      margin: 2rem 0 0.8rem;
    }

    .legal-content h2 { font-size: clamp(1.9rem, 2.2vw, 2.4rem); }
    .legal-content h3 { font-size: clamp(1.7rem, 2vw, 2rem); margin-top: 1.6rem; }
    .legal-content p, .legal-content li { font-size: 1.6rem; line-height: 1.4; color: #1f2937; }
    .legal-content p { margin: 0 0 1rem; }
    .legal-content ul { margin: 0 0 1rem; padding-left: 2rem; display: grid; gap: 0.35rem; }
    .legal-content a { color: var(--color-primary); text-decoration: underline; text-underline-offset: 2px; word-break: break-word; }
  </style>
</SiteLayout>
